OL,3,CNewcastle City Council budget: Tax
OL,4,Crises and #15million of cuts approved
OL,6,FNewcastle City Council has approved
OL,7,Fits budget for the coming year -
OL,8,Ffeaturing council tax rises and
OL,9,Fspending cuts.
OL,11,FOfficials had previously said that
OL,12,F"tough" decisions would be necessary
OL,13,Fto avoid following other local
OL,14,Fauthorities around the country into
OL,15,Feffective bankruptcy.
OL,17,FThe Labour-run council has warned that
OL,18,Fit must find #60 million worth of
OL,19,Fsavings by 2027 to balance its books,
OL,20,Fincluding #14.4 million over the next
OL,21,F12 months.
