OL,3,CNewcastle City Council budget: Tax
OL,4,Crises and #15million of cuts approved
OL,6,FProposals to reduce council spending
OL,7,Fwere signed off by councillors on
OL,8,FWednesday night. Cuts of #15million
OL,9,Fhave been approved while council tax
OL,10,Fwill rise by 4.99% - the maximum
OL,11,Fpermitted amount.
OL,13,FCrisis support services and a scheme
OL,14,Fproviding basic items for people in
OL,15,Fpoverty will be hit by the cuts, while
OL,16,Fresidents also face higher charges for
OL,17,Freplacement bins, garden waste
OL,18,Fcollections and parking. A small
OL,19,Fnumber of job losses are also expected.
