OL,3,CNewcastle City Council budget: Tax
OL,4,Crises and #15million of cuts approved
OL,6,FThe authority agreed to spend #281
OL,7,Fmillion on vital public services and
OL,8,Finvest #155 million in capital
OL,9,Fprojects, including improvements to
OL,10,FNorthumberland Street, a new leisure
OL,11,Fcentre in West Denton and improvements
OL,12,Fto the Grainger Market.
