OL,3,CNewcastle City Council budget: Tax
OL,4,Crises and #15million of cuts approved
OL,6,FMuch of the attention on the cuts had
OL,7,Ffocused on a proposal that would have
OL,8,Fseen the council halve its spending on
OL,9,Fbeds and support services for homeless
OL,10,Fpeople ` a move charities branded as
OL,11,F"inhumane".
OL,13,FThat plan was paused last month
OL,14,Ffollowing the backlash but officials
OL,15,Fhave said they will still be putting
OL,16,Fthe service under review.
OL,18,FThe final budget proposals voted
OL,19,Fthrough by the council are:
