OL,3,CNewcastle City Council budget: Tax
OL,4,Crises and #15million of cuts approved
OL,6,F- A council tax rise of 4.99%,
OL,7,Fincluding a 2% precept towards the
OL,8,Fcost of adult social care, amounting
OL,9,Fto a yearly increase of between #63.85
OL,10,Fand #191.55 depending on your house's
OL,11,Fbanding
OL,13,F- Ceasing the council's crisis support
OL,14,Fservice, which has a #100,000 annual
OL,15,Fprovision to help people suffering
OL,16,Femergencies through circumstances
OL,17,Fincluding domestic violence and
OL,18,Ffinancial abuse
